OL,4,CSheffield Children's Hospital: Baby
OL,5,C'doing OK' after SMA drug first
OL,6, A two-month-old baby is "doing OK"
OL,7, after becoming one of the first
OL,8, patients in England to be treated with
OL,9, a potentially life-saving drug.
OL,11,FBaby Markuss, who has Type 1 spinal
OL,12,Fmuscular atrophy (SMA), was treated at
OL,13,FSheffield Children's Hospital.
OL,15,FThe drug has a list price of #1.79m per
OL,16,Fdose and was made available on the NHS
OL,17,Fafter a deal with the manufacturers.
OL,19,FThe British Medical Journal previously
OL,20,Fcalled it "the most expensive drug
OL,21,Fcourse of treatment ever" .
